dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line)  Lincoln County, WI 2007
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2007. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Lincoln_Hydro_2007.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Lincoln_HydroLine_2007' and 'Lincoln_HydroPoly_2007'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: http://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
